    "본문HTML": "<p>\n\n</p><p>   <img alt=\"AI리터러시_모두를 위한 AI with 구글\" src=\"/cmmn/fileView?path=/ckeditor//GENERALNOTICES&amp;physical=1777876842190.jpg&amp;contentType=image\" style=\"width: 1000px; height: 1414px;\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:15pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">동국대학교 캠퍼스타운에서는 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">AI </span></span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">기술에 대한 심리적 장벽을 허물고</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">, (</span></span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">예비</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">)</span></span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">창업가의 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">AI </span></span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">활용 역량 강화를 위한 </span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:15pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">『AI</span></span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">리터러시</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">_</span></span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">모두를 위한 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">AI with </span></span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">구글</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">』 </span></span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">교육 참가자를 다음과 같이 모집하오니 많은 관심과 참여 부탁드립니다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\">.</span></span></span></p>\n<div id=\"hwpEditorBoardContent\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> </p>\n<p class=\"0\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">모집개요</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">1) </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">모집대상 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">동국대학교 재학생</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">캠퍼스타운 입주기업</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">일반인 등</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">선착순 마감</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">)</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">2) </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">모집기간 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">공고일로부터 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;